fq-bin: fq-bin (jq for binary formats)
fq-bin:
fq-bin: fq is inspired by the jq tool and language and allows you to work
fq-bin: with binary formats in the same way. In addition to using jq
fq-bin: expressions it can also present decoded tree structures, transform,
fq-bin: slice and concatenate binary data. It supports nested formats and
fq-bin: features an interactive REPL with auto-completion.
fq-bin:
fq-bin: Originally designed to query and debug media codecs and containers
fq-bin: like MP4, FLAC, JPEG but supports many more formats.
fq-bin: Homepage: https://github.com/wader/fq
